  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://purl.org/memo#VariantInstance">
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A specific image derived from a meme template; the Manifestation level of the FRBR hierarchy. Represents a single scraped or documented instantiation of a MemeConcept.</rdfs:comment>
